            <sentence>
                <offset>189</offset>
                <text>He was born at 37 weeks of gestation by cesarian section due to failure to progress and fetal distress.</text>
                <annotation id="5">
                    <infon key="type">webanno.custom.Phenotypes</infon>
                    <infon key="HPOterm">http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/HP_0025116</infon>
                    <location length="14" offset="88"/>
                    <text>fetal distress</text>
                </annotation>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>293</offset>
                <text>He needed resuscitation and oxygen but did not need intubation.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>357</offset>
                <text>His Appearance, Pulse, Grimace, Activity, Respiration (APGAR) scores were unknown.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>440</offset>
                <text>His birth weight was 1.6 kg and he stayed in the SCBU for 3 weeks.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>507</offset>
                <text>No other neonatal or feeding problems were found.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>557</offset>
                <text>He had generalized tonic-clonic seizures, which are now under control.</text>
                <annotation id="6">
                    <infon key="type">webanno.custom.Phenotypes</infon>
                    <infon key="HPOterm">http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/HP_0025190</infon>
                    <location length="33" offset="7"/>
                    <text>generalized tonic-clonic seizures</text>
                </annotation>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>628</offset>
                <text>He had only 3 episodes of GTC.</text>
                <annotation id="7">
                    <infon key="type">webanno.custom.Phenotypes</infon>
                    <infon key="HPOterm">http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/HP_0002069</infon>
                    <infon key="Comment">! Abbreviation</infon>
                    <location length="3" offset="26"/>
                    <text>GTC</text>
                </annotation>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>659</offset>
                <text>His parents are first-degree cousins and have 2 healthy children.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>725</offset>
                <text>There is no history of abortion or miscarriage and there is no similar case in the family.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>817</offset>
                <text>On physical examination, his weight was 8.8 kg (&lt;&lt;3rd centile), height was 77 cm (&lt;&lt;3rd centile) and head circumference 51 cm (75th centile).</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
